    "title": "どーんと☆お任せあれ♪",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "早朝、用事があって整備中の\r\nトレーニングコースに来ていた時……。",
            "enText": "Earlier in the morning, I had come \nto the training course, which was \nundergoing maintenance…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "pathId": -8915404910949181655,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "（ガガガガガガガ――プスンッ……！）",
            "enText": "(Gah gah gah gah gah gah—psssssssssssss …!)",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "pathId": 3270135182236666098,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "整備士A",
            "enName": "Mechanic A",
            "jpText": "うわっ！　故障か？\r\n整地車が急に動かなくなっちまった……！",
            "enText": "Oh, no! What's wrong? My gravel truck \nsuddenly stopped working…!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "pathId": 4013288938507176202,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヒシアケボノ",
            "enName": "Hishi Akebono",
            "jpText": "……あれっ、まだ整備中？\r\nもしかしてなにかあったのー？",
            "enText": "… Oh, it's still under maintenance? \nIs there something wrong?",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "トラブルがあったみたいだ",
                    "enText": "Looks like there was trouble.",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "トラブルがあったみたいだよ",
                    "enText": "I think there's been trouble.",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
